    <abstract>
      <t>   This draft defines a new type of Outbound Route Filter (ORF), known
   as the VPN Prefix ORF.  The VPN Prefix ORF mechanism is applicable
   when VPN routes from different VRFs are exchanged through a single
   shared BGP session.

	 </t>
